      "bgName": "stage01"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（今日は夏フェスに出演するLizNoirの）\n（付き添いでビーチに来たんだが……）",
      "startTime": 3.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "はい、かき氷です\n{user}さん、あーんして下さい",
      "startTime": 8.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "い、いや、一人で食べられるから……",
      "startTime": 11.38478508,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "あれ～、照れてるんですかぁ？\n恥ずかしがらなくていいんですよ？",
      "startTime": 18.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり夏と言えばかき氷ですよね\nメロン味のかき氷、甘くて冷たくて美味しいですよ～",
      "startTime": 25.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "溶けちゃう前にこころが食べさせてあげますね\nお口を開けて……はい、あーん",
      "startTime": 34.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（まいったな……どうしてこんなことに……）",
      "startTime": 39.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――時間は遡って、夏フェスの数週間前",
      "startTime": 44.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "リズノワの四人で沖縄に行きたいので\nスケジュールの調整をお願いしま～す",
      "startTime": 50.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "沖縄って……\n莉央さんと葵は新曲作りで忙しいんじゃないのか？",
      "startTime": 55.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "その曲作りで行き詰まってるから\n気持ちを切り替えるために合宿するんです",
      "startTime": 62.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "合宿だったら沖縄じゃなくてもいいだろ\n行き先が夏の沖縄なんて遊ぶ気まんまんじゃないか",
      "startTime": 68.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "分かってないですね～\nいい曲を作るために、夏の沖縄に行くんですよ",
      "startTime": 74.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんと葵さんはデビューしてすぐ人気になったから\n今まで海で遊ぶ暇がなかったんです",
      "startTime": 81.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "海で遊んだ経験がないのに\n夏の曲なんて作れる訳ないじゃないですかぁ",
      "startTime": 87.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "つーまーりー、夏の曲を作るためには\nまず夏の海を満喫する必要があるんです！",
      "startTime": 95.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "「新曲を書かないと、ツアーが出来ないわ！\nそのためには気高く沖縄で合宿するしかないのよっ」",
      "startTime": 102.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "……って莉央さんも言ってました～",
      "startTime": 107.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（いや、それは絶対に嘘だろう……）",
      "startTime": 109.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "でも確かに、沖縄の夏を体験することは\n難航している曲作りのヒントになるかもしれないな",
      "startTime": 115.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "そう思いますよね？\nだから、スケジュールの調整をお願いしま～す",
      "startTime": 120.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "分かった。みんなで沖縄へ行けるように調整するよ",
      "startTime": 124.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr014.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます！\n持つべきものはチョロいマネージャーさんですね",
      "startTime": 130.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "チョロいって……まぁいいか。それじゃあ俺も\n一緒に行けるように仕事を片付けておかないとな",
      "startTime": 138.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr015.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？　{user}さんも\n沖縄について来る気なんですか？",
      "startTime": 143.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr016.m4a",
      "text": "旅費さえ出してくれたら、{user}さんは\nいなくてもいいんですけど……",
      "startTime": 149.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん以外は未成年なんだから\n大人が同行した方がいいだろ？",
      "startTime": 154.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr017.m4a",
      "text": "保護者なら莉央さんがいるから大丈夫ですよ～",
      "startTime": 156.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "でも葵と愛とこころの面倒を\n莉央さん一人で見るのは大変じゃないか？",
      "startTime": 162.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr018.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん以外\n全員問題児みたいに言わないで下さーい！",
      "startTime": 166.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr019.m4a",
      "text": "それに、夏の新曲を作るために\nこころ達は沖縄の海を満喫しなくちゃいけないんです",
      "startTime": 172.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr020.m4a",
      "text": "それなのにマネージャーさんが一緒だったら\n羽を伸ばして遊べないじゃないですか",
      "startTime": 180.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱ遊ぶ気まんまんじゃないか……\nだったら、みんなには内緒でついて行くよ",
      "startTime": 186.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "気付かれないように後をつけて、何かあった時は\nこっそりフォローする。それならいいだろ？",
      "startTime": 192.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr021.m4a",
      "text": "……つまり、こころ達をストーキングして\nプライベートの水着姿をこっそり覗き見したいと……",
      "startTime": 199.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_04_01-kkr022.m4a",
      "text": "……盗撮は犯罪ですよ？",
      "startTime": 204.6333333333,
